  "description": "🚀 AI-Powered Stock Analysis Chatbot\n\nTransform Your Investment Decisions with Advanced AI Analytics\n\n🎯 What It Does\nThis intelligent chatbot leverages cutting-edge financial APIs and AI-driven analysis to deliver comprehensive stock research reports. Get instant access to professional-grade investment analysis that combines multiple data sources for informed decision-making.\n\n✨ Key Features\n\n📊 AI-Driven Stock Scoring\nPowered by Danelfin's proprietary AI algorithms\nReal-time scoring across 5 key metrics: AI Score, Technical, Fundamental, Sentiment, and Low-Risk ratings\nAccess to comprehensive stock rankings and sector analysis\n\n📈 Advanced Technical Analysis\nIntegration with TwelveData for precise technical indicators\nBollinger Bands, MACD, RSI, and moving averages analysis\nHistorical price data and trend identification\n\n🖼️ Visual Chart Integration\nAutomatic generation of professional candlestick charts\nChart-img API integration for clear visual representations\nCharts embedded directly in analysis reports\n\n📰 Sentiment Analysis\nAlpha Vantage news sentiment scoring\nMarket intelligence and sentiment tracking\nReal-time news impact assessment\n\n🧠 Vector-Powered Intelligence\nSupabase vector storage for pattern recognition\nAdvanced data correlation and historical analysis\nIntelligent recommendation engine\n\n📋 What You Get\n\nComprehensive Markdown Reports Including:\nExecutive Summary** with actionable insights\nDetailed Stock Analysis** with AI scoring breakdown\nInteractive Charts** for each analyzed stock\nTechnical Indicators** and trend analysis\nCurrent Stock Prices** and market data\nRisk Assessment** and sentiment evaluation\nInvestment Recommendations** tailored to your strategy\n\n🎯 Perfect For\nIndividual Investors** seeking professional-grade analysis\nFinancial Advisors** needing quick research reports\nPortfolio Managers** requiring data-driven insights\nDay Traders** looking for technical analysis\nLong-term Investors** focused on fundamental analysis\n\n🔧 How It Works\nAsk About Any Stock - Simply mention a ticker or describe your investment criteria\nAI Screening - The bot queries multiple APIs to gather comprehensive data\nAdvanced Analysis - Technical indicators, sentiment, and AI scoring are processed\nProfessional Report - Receive a detailed markdown report with charts and recommendations\nInstant Delivery - Get results in seconds, not hours\n\n🛡️ Data Sources & Reliability\nDanelfin**: AI-powered stock scoring and rankings\nTwelveData**: Professional-grade market data and technical indicators\nAlpha Vantage**: News sentiment and market intelligence\nChart-img**: High-quality financial chart generation\nSupabase**: Advanced vector database for pattern analysis\n\n💡 Sample Use Cases\n\"Analyze the top 3 tech stocks with highest AI scores\"\n\"Find low-risk dividend stocks in the utilities sector\"\n\"Compare AAPL vs MSFT with technical analysis\"\n\"Show me growth stocks with strong buy signals\"\n\"Analyze energy sector performance this week\"\n\n",
  "createdAt": "2025-08-11T18:21:35.421Z",
